Key Match Events: Victor Wembanyama delivered an impressive 29-point performance, shooting 10-of-17 from the field, adding seven rebounds and three blocks.
Wembanyama knocked down two of his five three-point attempts and went 7-of-8 from the line.
The Spurs built a solid lead, going up by 22 points before the Rockets tried to claw their way back with a huge fourth quarter.
